						               													<description>Welcome to Boy Band Builder:  The Card Game.  A Fun &amp;amp; Fast Paced Game for 2-4 Players, 15-30 Minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game Description:&amp;#10;Now you can build and manage the Boyband of your Dreams.  Develop new artists, build your group, and spin it into solid gold!  Recruit boys to enhance your group. The boys feature 4 characteristics (Pipes, Moves,Heat, and Cool) which can be enhanced with Star Cards.  You can throw shade at the competition and fight for all all the best Gigs.  It&amp;rsquo;s a cutthroat business, do you have what it takes to make it to the top?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay:&amp;#10;Players take turns in sequence and may take two actions per turn from a range of options.  Players can recruit Artists for their band, draw two Star Cards into their hand, play a Star Card on an artist or band, or do a Gig.  Players are trying to do all the best gigs before the competition, so they must play Star Cards on their artists to buff them up enough to do the gig. The combination and order of actions is critical to building a band with the stats you need and handle the negative Star Cards coming from your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the Gig deck runs dry, whoever has done the most Gigs and made the most $ wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
